On 6 April 2018, at approximately 23:50 Louis en Thea Rautenbach were attacked at Jock of the Bushveld chalets, R40, Barberton. Thea’s son was stabbed in the face during the attack on the farm and is not in a serious condition. The police are investigating, there have been no arrests. Read the original article in Afrikaans on BKA Boere Krisis Aksie 